on a lecture trip and has just returned I had a letter from him just after he was at Laurel Nebr. He said he saw Miss Fish there and that she talked just as fast as she could asking question about us all <unclear/> included, I wish he could get to your town once. I had a letter from Mrs. Bailey and she asked about you too Mrs. White is very delicate Mrs. Bailey seemed worried about her. Please write me soon and tell me all you have him doing remember me to all your people Especially to your good father and mother. 
Poor Mrs. Brown is thinking of going back to teaching again. She seems to be unable to make ends meet. Ruth is in High School Mrs. Ward is still teaching. 
Dear girls you know I love you Ever tho I have been so mean about writing and please heap <unclear/> of fere on my head by writing soon lots of love Alice Neihardt 